            INTERNAL FUNCTION (ARR,N)
            ENTRY TO INSORT.
            THROUGH LOOP1, FOR I=1, 1, I.GE.N
            KEY=ARR(I)
            J=I-1
INNER       WHENEVER J.L.0.OR.ARR(J).LE.KEY, TRANSFER TO PLACE
            ARR(J+1)=ARR(J)
            J=J-1
            TRANSFER TO INNER
PLACE       ARR(J+1)=KEY
LOOP1       CONTINUE
            FUNCTION RETURN
            END OF FUNCTION
